This is an example template for booking terms

Booking

You can book classes one day in advance, but no later than 30 minutes before the class starts. To get your ticket, register your member card
in a reader no later than 5 minutes before the class

Cancellation

Cancel your booking no later than one hour before the class if you cannot attend. If you miss three classes you can no longer book online without paying a fee.
